Usually a corner of the game is a safe initial click point, because in most minesweeping game designs, the first click will not trigger a mine.
To select the position in the upper left corner and click, the following operations are possible:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 320, "height": 235}}
]
```
